column5: I was there today and discovered the flea market upstairs. I was like a kid in a candy store, full dash assemblies with guages for 150 - 250, seats, and seat posts, misc parts out the wazzo! And very good prices too. The people behind the counter were very helpful as well.
Oh ya, been there a few times for stuff that's "obsolete" or if you're making your own dash or electrical system.
